687
00:37:34.710 --> 00:37:36.258
The main reason I believe

688
00:37:36.300 --> 00:37:38.838
that these are simply future humans

689
00:37:38.880 --> 00:37:41.268
or extratempestrial descendants

690
00:37:41.310 --> 00:37:43.038
is because if we look at the long history

691
00:37:43.080 --> 00:37:44.358
