692
00:37:44.400 --> 00:37:47.628
the main trends are
an increase in brain size

693
00:37:47.670 --> 00:37:49.548
and reduction in our facial anatomy.

694
00:37:49.590 --> 00:37:52.578
or a shift toward
orthognathism as we call it.

695
00:37:52.620 --> 00:37:55.758
That has occurred in
concert with standing upright.

696
00:37:55.800 --> 00:37:57.828
Our heads had to rotate down

697
00:37:57.870 --> 00:37:58.878
to see where we were going

698
00:37:58.920 --> 00:38:02.388
once we became bipedal
six to eight million years ago.

699
00:38:02.430 --> 00:38:06.078
And doing that. it caused
our basicranium to flex

700
00:38:06.120 --> 00:38:07.548
and that opened up more space

701
00:38:07.590 --> 00:38:10.038
