705
00:38:17.010 --> 00:38:18.348
and we had fire.

706
00:38:18.390 --> 00:38:20.778
that released our faces

707
00:38:20.820 --> 00:38:23.178
of the burdens of chewing. mastication.

708
00:38:23.220 --> 00:38:25.788
