710
00:38:28.110 --> 00:38:30.678
Height is an interesting characteristic.

711
00:38:30.720 --> 00:38:33.708
It's actually very much
influenced by the environment.

712
00:38:33.750 --> 00:38:35.748
So. for instance. after
the Great Depression.

713
00:38:35.790 --> 00:38:37.218
during times of warfare

714
00:38:37.260 --> 00:38:40.038
when resources are in scarce supply.

715
00:38:40.080 --> 00:38:42.078
we actually become much shorter.

716
00:38:42.120 --> 00:38:43.998
And when there's more food available.

717
00:38:44.040 --> 00:38:45.678
when the population's healthy.

718
00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:46.878
